 Stonebowy and Wife Dr. Louisa Ghanaian dancehall artist, Stonebowy’s wife Dr Mrs Louisa Satekla (nee Ansong), turned a year older on Tuesday, January 19, 2021. In celebration of her birthday, Stonebowy and Dr Mrs Louis have flown out of Accra to USA for what seems to be a vacation. Mrs Louise took to her Instagram page to share updates of their travel, posting a photo of them in a business class onboard, she wrote “birthday behaviour” to the photo that was shared with John F. Kennedy International Airport as the geotag location. Stonebwoy, and his wife Dr Louisa, got married in June 2017 and they have two children, Jidula Catherine Setakla and Janam Livingstone Jnr, together.